OperationQueue:
Implements a queue which allows one async call to block a series of other calls.

Install:
- Move operation-queue.js into application source tree.
- Include operation-queue.js via sources.json

Usage:
- See OperationQueue instance methods.

Related Files:
- operation-queue-test.js : Automated test of this component.

History:
 - 4/24/2010
      Version 1.0
